{"tid":515991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩警告︰美國全境都在北韓核武器的攻擊範圍內","createTime":"2018-01-01T02:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T10:38:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"feeb2991b645d1b969959e5c27b848ea4b6f99ef","tid":515991,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:08:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】北韓領袖金正恩發表新年講話，警告美國全境都在北韓核武器的攻擊範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩在新年講話中，宣稱完成國家核武力建設的歷史大業，美國必須明白這個事實，又說未來會集中部署核彈頭和彈道導彈。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩警告整個美國都在北韓的核武攻擊範圍內，美國不會有能力向北韓發動戰爭，而啟動核武的按鈕一直都在他的桌上，他強調這個是事實，並非威嚇。<br />\n<br />\n不過，金正恩亦提到北韓和南韓應該改善關係，雙方對話的道路是打開的，他又說正考慮派代表團參加南韓主辦的冬季奧運會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=248826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248826&d=dBgBEzGz4KVohpnrt7fpUozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e1ffdce1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248826&h=2484b633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=248826</a>"},{"pid":"b5115b0d6bdc6eef705b9e286ef8a587d71d81c2","tid":515991,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:09:34.000Z","msg":"新年就講可以全境襲擊美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1de6f7c65e981294ef1343453ac3cb50c69225","tid":515991,"uid":123859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"認真香港九龍無得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c6304e5f2b723e00a39d21e9c63c9085185ff4","tid":515991,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"開年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a34e14c0c6ba944c885d34f6fae9c2c5414056","tid":515991,"uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:13:25.000Z",